Film Cam Privacy Policy

introduction

Private information refers to the secrets in the personal life of citizens that are unwilling to be disclosed or known to others. Film Cam (referring to 2022 studio, the same below) attaches great importance to the protection of user privacy information. When you use Film Cam products and services, Film Cam may collect and use your relevant information. The Film Cam hopes to explain to you the information that the Film Cam may collect (including the collection method), the purpose of collecting this information, the Film Cam and how you can protect the security of this information through this policy. Please read this policy carefully before using all products and services of the Film Cam, and be sure to understand our rules for handling your personal information. If you have any questions about this privacy agreement, you can contact us for consultation. If you do not agree with any of the terms in this privacy agreement, you should immediately stop using Film Cam products and services. Once you choose to use or continue to use the Film Cam products and services after the Film Cam has updated this privacy policy (the Film Cam will prompt you to update it in a timely manner), it means that you acknowledge and accept all the contents of this policy (including the updated version), and Agree to the collection, use, storage and sharing of information about you by Film Cam in accordance with this policy.

